### Base URL (change this based on your environment)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### 1. Create a palindrome string
POST {{baseUrl}}/strings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": "racecar"
}

### 2. Create a normal string
POST {{baseUrl}}/strings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": "hello world"
}

### 3. Create another palindrome
POST {{baseUrl}}/strings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": "madam"
}

### 4. Create a multi-word palindrome
POST {{baseUrl}}/strings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": "noon"
}

### 5. Try to create duplicate (should get 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/strings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": "racecar"
}

### 6. Get specific string
GET {{baseUrl}}/strings/racecar

### 7. Get all strings
GET {{baseUrl}}/strings

### 8. Get palindromes only
GET {{baseUrl}}/strings?is_palindrome=true

### 9. Get strings with exact word count
GET {{baseUrl}}/strings?word_count=2

### 10. Get strings with min/max length
GET {{baseUrl}}/strings?min_length=5&max_length=10

### 11. Get strings containing specific character
GET {{baseUrl}}/strings?contains_character=a

### 12. Combined filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/strings?is_palindrome=true&word_count=1

### 13. Natural language query - single word palindromes
GET {{baseUrl}}/strings/filter-by-natural-language?query=all single word palindromic strings

### 14. Natural language query - strings longer than
GET {{baseUrl}}/strings/filter-by-natural-language?query=strings longer than 5 characters

### 15. Natural language query - contains letter
GET {{baseUrl}}/strings/filter-by-natural-language?query=strings containing the letter a

### 16. Delete a string
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/strings/racecar

### 17. Try to get deleted string (should get 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/strings/racecar

### 18. Try to delete non-existent string (should get 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/strings/nonexistent

### 19. Invalid request - missing value field (should get 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/strings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wrong_field": "test"
}

### 20. Invalid query parameter (should get 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/strings?min_length=-5

